      <title>戴蒙称推动停止所有石油、天然气项目的做法极其幼稚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/dimon-calls-push-to-stop-all-oil-gas-projects-enormously-naive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰米戴蒙表示，美国推迟液化天然气项目是出于“政治原因”，以安抚那些认为应该停止石油和天然气项目的人——他称这种立场“错误”且“极其天真”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/dimon-calls-push-to-stop-all-oil-gas-projects-enormously-naive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 16:25:14 GMT</pubDate>
